    <main>
        <section class="section">
            <div class="container">
                <div
                    class="row">
                    <!-- ════════════════════════════════════
                         MAIN COLUMN
                    ════════════════════════════════════ -->
                    <div
                        class="col-lg-8">
                        <!-- ── Video Callout ── -->
                        <div class="video-callout">
                            <span class="eyebrow">Independent Contractor Opportunity</span>
                            <h2>Want to add 3–5 weekly cleans?</h2>
                            <p class="video-subhead">Watch this first</p>
                            <div class="video-wrapper">
                                <video controls>
                                    <source src="https://pub-8240a48ff747403ab36500bc6295feea.r2.dev/cleaners.mov" type="video/mp4"> Your browser doesn't
                                    support video playback.
                                </video>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- ── Opportunity Overview ── -->
                        <div class="opportunity-section">
                            <h2 class="mb-3">Partner with Minty Clean</h2>
                            <p>
                                We're a Tucson residential cleaning company that handles the bookings, the clients, and the scheduling. You handle the
                                cleaning. It's a 1099 contractor relationship — you're running your own operation, and we're running ours. We pay our
                                cleaning partners well because good work deserves it.
                            </p>
                            <p class="mt-3">
                                Partners who show up reliably and take pride in their work get consistent jobs. Partners who don't meet our standards
                                don't stay on. We're straightforward about that because it's better for everyone - especially the people who are serious
                                about doing this well.
                            </p>
                            <p class="mt-3">
                                This is a professional operation. Every job has client-facing expectations — things like wearing shoe coverings, doing a
                                walkthrough with the client at the end of each clean, arriving on time, and representing Minty Clean while you're on the
                                job. Not unreasonable asks. Just the standard we hold ourselves to.
                            </p>
                            <!-- Legal disclosure -->
                            <div class="legal-disclosure">
                                <strong>Independent Contractor Notice:</strong>
                                This is not an employment position. Contractors are self-employed and responsible for their own taxes, insurance, and
                                equipment. You will receive a Form 1099 at year-end if earnings meet IRS thresholds.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- ── Benefits ── -->
                        <div class="benefits-section">
                            <span class="subtitle">Why Work With Us</span>
                            <h3>What you get out of this</h3>
                            <p class="section-intro">Beyond the flexibility of being your own boss, partnering with Minty Clean solves the hardest
                                parts of running an independent cleaning operation.</p>
                            <div class="benefits-grid">
                                <div class="benefit-item">
                                    <i class="bi bi-calendar2-week text-success"></i>
                                    <div>
                                        <strong>Regular, reliable workflow</strong>
                                        <p>We keep a full book of recurring clients. Good partners don't scramble for work - it comes to them.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="benefit-item">
                                    <i class="bi bi-megaphone text-success"></i>
                                    <div>
                                        <strong>No lead generation on your end</strong>
                                        <p>We handle all the marketing, advertising, and client acquisition. You just clean. Zero time or money spent chasing
                                            new customers.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="benefit-item">
                                    <i class="bi bi-cash-coin text-success"></i>
                                    <div>
                                        <strong>Premium pay per job</strong>
                                        <p>We pay above-market rates because we want serious people. If you do good work, you'll earn well here.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="benefit-item">
                                    <i class="bi bi-clock text-success"></i>
                                    <div>
                                        <strong>Set your own schedule</strong>
                                        <p>Take jobs when you want them. No mandatory shifts, no minimum hours. You're in control of your time.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="benefit-item">
                                    <i class="bi bi-receipt text-success"></i>
                                    <div>
                                        <strong>No invoicing or chasing payments</strong>
                                        <p>We handle all client billing and collections. You get paid for your work, cleanly and on time.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="benefit-item">
                                    <i class="bi bi-people text-success"></i>
                                    <div>
                                        <strong>Freedom to work elsewhere</strong>
                                        <p>We don't require exclusivity. Work with other clients or companies on your own time - that's your business.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="benefit-item">
                                    <i class="bi bi-graph-up-arrow text-success"></i>
                                    <div>
                                        <strong>Opportunity to grow with us</strong>
                                        <p>As we expand, our best partners get first access to more jobs, new service areas, and higher-value clients.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="benefit-item">
                                    <i class="bi bi-shield-check text-success"></i>
                                    <div>
                                        <strong>Vetted, trustworthy clients</strong>
                                        <p>We screen our customers. You show up to homes where you're expected, welcomed, and respected.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- ── Application Form ── -->
                        <div class="form-container">
                            <div class="text-center mb-5" id="form-header">
                                <span class="subtitle">Contractor Application</span>
                                <h2 class="mb-4">Apply to Partner with Minty Clean</h2>
                                <h5 class="text-muted fw-normal mb-4">Tell us about your experience and how you work</h5>
                                <p class="text-muted">
                                    This form takes about 10 minutes. We review every application and reach out to qualified candidates within a few
                                    business days.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <hr>
                            <form
                                id="careerForm" novalidate>
                                <!-- ── Personal Information ── -->
                                <h3 class="form-section-title">Personal Information</h3>
                                <div class="row g-3 mb-4">
                                    <div class="col-md-6">
                                        <label for="firstName" class="form-label">First Name
                                            <span class="text-danger">*</span>
                                        </label>
                                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="firstName" name="firstName" required placeholder="Enter your first name">
                                        <div class="invalid-feedback">Please enter your first name.</div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-md-6">
                                        <label for="lastName" class="form-label">Last Name
                                            <span class="text-danger">*</span>
                                        </label>
                                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="lastName" name="lastName" required placeholder="Enter your last name">
                                        <div class="invalid-feedback">Please enter your last name.</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row g-3 mb-4">
                                    <div class="col-md-6">
                                        <label for="email" class="form-label">Email
                                            <span class="text-danger">*</span>
                                        </label>
                                        <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" name="email" required placeholder="Enter your email">
                                        <div class="invalid-feedback">Please enter a valid email.</div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-md-6">
                                        <label for="phone" class="form-label">Phone Number
                                            <span class="text-danger">*</span>
                                        </label>
                                        <input
                                            type="tel"
                                            class="form-control"
                                            id="phone"
                                            name="phone"
                                            required
                                            placeholder="Enter your phone number"
                                            pattern="[0-9\s\-\(\)\+\.]{10,20}">
                                        <div class="invalid-feedback">Please enter a valid phone number.</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row g-3 mb-4">
                                    <div class="col-md-5">
                                        <label for="city" class="form-label">City
                                            <span class="text-danger">*</span>
                                        </label>
                                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="city" name="city" required placeholder="City">
                                        <div class="invalid-feedback">Please enter your city.</div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-md-3">
                                        <label for="state" class="form-label">State
                                            <span class="text-danger">*</span>
                                        </label>
                                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="state" name="state" required placeholder="State">
                                        <div class="invalid-feedback">Please enter your state.</div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-md-4">
                                        <label for="zipcode" class="form-label">ZIP Code
                                            <span class="text-danger">*</span>
                                        </label>
                                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="zipcode" name="zipcode" required placeholder="ZIP code">
                                        <div class="invalid-feedback">Please enter your ZIP code.</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <!-- ── Transportation & Service Area ── -->
                                <h3 class="form-section-title">Transportation & Service Area</h3>
                                <div class="mb-4">
                                    <label class="form-label">Do you have reliable personal transportation?
                                        <span class="text-danger">*</span>
                                    </label>
                                    <small class="d-block text-muted mb-2">You'll need your own vehicle to travel between client homes</small>
                                    <div class="row g-2">
                                        <div class="col-6 col-md-3">
                                            <input type="radio" class="btn-check" name="transportation" id="transYes" value="true" required>
                                            <label class="btn w-100" for="transYes">Yes</label>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-6 col-md-3">
                                            <input type="radio" class="btn-check" name="transportation" id="transNo" value="false">
                                            <label class="btn w-100" for="transNo">No</label>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="invalid-feedback" style="display:none;" id="transportationError">Please select an option.</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-4">
                                    <label for="serviceRadius" class="form-label">How far are you willing to travel for jobs?
                                        <span class="text-danger">*</span>
                                    </label>
                                    <select class="form-select" id="serviceRadius" name="serviceRadius" required>
                                        <option value="">Select a range</option>
                                        <option value="5">Up to 5 miles</option>
                                        <option value="10">Up to 10 miles</option>
                                        <option value="20">Up to 20 miles</option>
                                        <option value="any">Anywhere in Tucson metro</option>
                                    </select>
                                    <div class="invalid-feedback">Please select your travel range.</div>
                                </div>
                                <!-- ── Availability ── -->
                                <h3 class="form-section-title">Availability</h3>
                                <div class="mb-4">
                                    <label for="jobsPerWeek" class="form-label">How many jobs per week are you looking to take on?
                                        <span class="text-danger">*</span>
                                    </label>
                                    <select class="form-select" id="jobsPerWeek" name="jobsPerWeek" required>
                                        <option value="">Select an estimate</option>
                                        <option value="1-3">1–3 jobs/week</option>
                                        <option value="4-6">4–6 jobs/week</option>
                                        <option value="7-10">7–10 jobs/week</option>
                                        <option value="10+">10+ jobs/week</option>
                                    </select>
                                    <div class="invalid-feedback">Please select your preferred job volume.</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-4">
                                    <label for="startDate" class="form-label">When are you available to start taking jobs?
                                        <span class="text-danger">*</span>
                                    </label>
                                    <input type="date" class="form-control" id="startDate" name="startDate" required>
                                    <div class="invalid-feedback">Please select a start date.</div>
                                </div>
                                <!-- ── Business & Contractor Status ── -->
                                <h3 class="form-section-title">Business & Contractor Status</h3>
                                <p class="text-muted mb-3" style="font-size:0.9rem;">
                                    These questions help us understand your setup as an independent contractor.
                                </p>
                                <div class="mb-4">
                                    <label class="form-label">Do you currently operate as a sole proprietor or registered business?
                                        <span class="text-danger">*</span>
                                    </label>
                                    <div class="row g-2">
                                        <div class="col-6 col-md-4">
                                            <input type="radio" class="btn-check" name="businessStatus" id="bizSole" value="sole_proprietor" required>
                                            <label class="btn w-100" for="bizSole">Sole Proprietor</label>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-6 col-md-4">
                                            <input type="radio" class="btn-check" name="businessStatus" id="bizRegistered" value="registered_business">
                                            <label class="btn w-100" for="bizRegistered">Registered Business</label>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-6 col-md-4">
                                            <input type="radio" class="btn-check" name="businessStatus" id="bizNeither" value="neither">
                                            <label class="btn w-100" for="bizNeither">Neither / Not Sure</label>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="invalid-feedback" style="display:none;" id="businessStatusError">Please select an option.</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-4">
                                    <label class="form-label">Do you currently provide cleaning services to other clients outside of Minty Clean?
                                        <span class="text-danger">*</span>
                                    </label>
                                    <small class="d-block text-muted mb-2">This is completely fine - we don't require exclusivity</small>
                                    <div class="row g-2">
                                        <div class="col-6 col-md-3">
                                            <input type="radio" class="btn-check" name="otherClients" id="otherYes" value="true" required>
                                            <label class="btn w-100" for="otherYes">Yes</label>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-6 col-md-3">
                                            <input type="radio" class="btn-check" name="otherClients" id="otherNo" value="false">
                                            <label class="btn w-100" for="otherNo">No</label>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="invalid-feedback" style="display:none;" id="otherClientsError">Please select an option.</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-4">
                                    <label class="form-label">Do you carry your own general liability insurance?
                                        <span class="text-danger">*</span>
                                    </label>
                                    <small class="d-block text-muted mb-2">Preferred but not currently required to apply</small>
                                    <div class="row g-2">
                                        <div class="col-6 col-md-3">
                                            <input type="radio" class="btn-check" name="insurance" id="insYes" value="true" required>
                                            <label class="btn w-100" for="insYes">Yes</label>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-6 col-md-3">
                                            <input type="radio" class="btn-check" name="insurance" id="insNo" value="false">
                                            <label class="btn w-100" for="insNo">No</label>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="invalid-feedback" style="display:none;" id="insuranceError">Please select an option.</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-4">
                                    <label class="form-label">Do you have your own cleaning supplies and equipment?
                                        <span class="text-danger">*</span>
                                    </label>
                                    <small class="d-block text-muted mb-2">Note: Minty Clean may supply specific products for brand consistency on certain
                                        jobs</small>
                                    <div class="row g-2">
                                        <div class="col-6 col-md-3">
                                            <input type="radio" class="btn-check" name="ownSupplies" id="suppliesYes" value="true" required>
                                            <label class="btn w-100" for="suppliesYes">Yes</label>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-6 col-md-3">
                                            <input type="radio" class="btn-check" name="ownSupplies" id="suppliesNo" value="false">
                                            <label class="btn w-100" for="suppliesNo">No</label>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="invalid-feedback" style="display:none;" id="suppliesError">Please select an option.</div>
                                </div>
                                <!-- ── Experience & Skills ── -->
                                <h3 class="form-section-title">Experience & Skills</h3>
                                <div class="mb-4">
                                    <label class="form-label">Do you have professional cleaning experience?
                                        <span class="text-danger">*</span>
                                    </label>
                                    <div class="row g-2">
                                        <div class="col-6 col-md-3">
                                            <input type="radio" class="btn-check" name="experience" id="expYes" value="true" required>
                                            <label class="btn w-100" for="expYes">Yes</label>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-6 col-md-3">
                                            <input type="radio" class="btn-check" name="experience" id="expNo" value="false">
                                            <label class="btn w-100" for="expNo">No</label>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="invalid-feedback" style="display:none;" id="experienceError">Please select an option.</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-4">
                                    <label for="experienceDetails" class="form-label">Describe your cleaning experience</label>
                                    <small class="d-block text-muted mb-2">Where you've worked, for how long, and what kind of cleaning (residential,
                                        commercial, etc.)</small>
                                    <textarea class="form-control" id="experienceDetails" name="experienceDetails" rows="4"></textarea>
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-4">
                                    <label class="form-label">Are you comfortable cleaning homes with pets?</label>
                                    <div class="row g-2">
                                        <div class="col-6 col-md-3">
                                            <input type="radio" class="btn-check" name="pets" id="petsYes" value="true">
                                            <label class="btn w-100" for="petsYes">Yes</label>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-6 col-md-3">
                                            <input type="radio" class="btn-check" name="pets" id="petsNo" value="false">
                                            <label class="btn w-100" for="petsNo">No</label>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-4">
                                    <label for="serviceTypes" class="form-label">What types of cleaning are you comfortable with?</label>
                                    <small class="d-block text-muted mb-2">Select all that apply</small>
                                    <div class="row g-2">
                                        <div class="col-6 col-md-6">
                                            <div class="form-check">
                                                <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="svcStandard" name="serviceTypes" value="standard">
                                                <label class="form-check-label" for="svcStandard">Standard recurring clean</label>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-6 col-md-6">
                                            <div class="form-check">
                                                <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="svcDeep" name="serviceTypes" value="deep">
                                                <label class="form-check-label" for="svcDeep">Deep clean</label>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-6 col-md-6">
                                            <div class="form-check">
                                                <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="svcMoveout" name="serviceTypes" value="moveout">
                                                <label class="form-check-label" for="svcMoveout">Move-in / move-out clean</label>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-6 col-md-6">
                                            <div class="form-check">
                                                <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="svcPostconstruction" name="serviceTypes" value="postconstruction">
                                                <label class="form-check-label" for="svcPostconstruction">Post-construction clean</label>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <!-- ── Additional Information ── -->
                                <h3 class="form-section-title">Additional Information</h3>
                                <div class="mb-4">
                                    <label for="whyWork" class="form-label">Why are you interested in contracting with Minty Clean?
                                        <span class="text-danger">*</span>
                                    </label>
                                    <textarea class="form-control" id="whyWork" name="whyWork" rows="4" required></textarea>
                                    <div class="invalid-feedback">Please tell us why you're interested.</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-4">
                                    <label for="strengths" class="form-label">What makes you a reliable, high-quality cleaner?</label>
                                    <textarea class="form-control" id="strengths" name="strengths" rows="3"></textarea>
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-4">
                                    <label for="hearAbout" class="form-label">How did you hear about this opportunity?</label>
                                    <select class="form-select" id="hearAbout" name="hearAbout">
                                        <option value="">Select an option</option>
                                        <option value="website">Minty Clean Website</option>
                                        <option value="indeed">Indeed</option>
                                        <option value="craigslist">Craigslist</option>
                                        <option value="facebook">Facebook</option>
                                        <option value="referral">Referral from someone I know</option>
                                        <option value="other">Other</option>
                                    </select>
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-4">
                                    <label for="additionalInfo" class="form-label">Anything else you'd like us to know?</label>
                                    <textarea class="form-control" id="additionalInfo" name="additionalInfo" rows="3"></textarea>
                                </div>
                                <!-- ── Acknowledgment ── -->
                                <h3 class="form-section-title">Acknowledgment</h3>
                                <div class="mb-4">
                                    <div class="form-check">
                                        <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="ackContractor" name="ackContractor" required>
                                        <label class="form-check-label" for="ackContractor">
                                            I understand that this is an
                                            <strong>independent contractor opportunity</strong>, not an employment position. I am responsible for my own taxes,
                                                insurance, and equipment.
                                            <span class="text-danger">*</span>
                                        </label>
                                        <div class="invalid-feedback">You must acknowledge the contractor relationship to proceed.</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <!-- Submit -->
                                <div class="text-center mt-5">
                                    <button type="submit" class="btn">Submit Application</button>
                                    <p class="tos-text">
                                        By submitting, you confirm that all information provided is accurate and complete.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </form>
                            <!-- Success Message -->
                            <div id="successMessage" class="success-message" style="display:none;">
                                <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success"></i>
                                <h2>Application received!</h2>
                                <p class="lead mb-4">
                                    Thanks for your interest in partnering with Minty Clean. We'll review your application and reach out to qualified
                                    candidates to discuss next steps.
                                </p>
                                <div class="alert mb-0">
                                    Expect to hear back within 3–5 business days. Check your spam folder too!
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- ════════════════════════════════════
                         SIDEBAR
                    ════════════════════════════════════ -->
                    <div class="col-lg-4 d-none d-lg-block">
                        <div class="sidebar-element">
                            <i class="bi bi-file-earmark-person"></i>
                            <strong>Apply</strong>
                            <p>Fill out the application below - it covers your experience, availability, and contractor setup.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="sidebar-element">
                            <i class="bi bi-chat-dots"></i>
                            <strong>We'll Reach Out</strong>
                            <p>We review every application and contact strong candidates to talk through the opportunity.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="sidebar-element">
                            <i class="bi bi-briefcase"></i>
                            <strong>Start Taking Jobs</strong>
                            <p>Once onboarded, you'll get access to our scheduling app and can start picking up jobs in your area.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="summary-box">
                            <h3>What We're Looking For</h3>
                            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                                <li class="mb-3">
                                    <i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success me-2"></i>
                                    <strong>Proven cleaning experience</strong>
                                </li>
                                <li class="mb-3">
                                    <i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success me-2"></i>
                                    <strong>Reliable transportation</strong>
                                </li>
                                <li class="mb-3">
                                    <i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success me-2"></i>
                                    <strong>Professional, client-facing attitude</strong>
                                </li>
                                <li class="mb-3">
                                    <i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success me-2"></i>
                                    <strong>Able to meet our service standards</strong>
                                </li>
                                <li class="mb-3">
                                    <i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success me-2"></i>
                                    <strong>Own supplies and equipment</strong>
                                </li>
                                <li class="mb-0">
                                    <i class="bi bi-check-circle text-success me-2"></i>
                                    <strong>Self-directed and accountable</strong>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <script>
            const MAKE_WEBHOOK_URL = 'https://hook.us2.make.com/u22ry2fdadl22en3l73f1jjod0s6z1nc';
            const form = document.getElementById('careerForm');
            // ── Radio group names that need custom validation ── Bootstrap's :invalid only works on inputs with `required`, but
            // radio groups need manual handling since only one input in the group carries `required`.
            const requiredRadioGroups = [
                'transportation',
                'businessStatus',
                'otherClients',
                'insurance',
                'ownSupplies',
                'experience'
            ];
            // ── Validate all radio groups and toggle their error messages ──
            function validateRadioGroups() {
                let allValid = true;
                requiredRadioGroups.forEach((name) => {
                    const selected = form.querySelector (`input[name="${name}"]:checked`);
                    // Error element ID convention: nameError (e.g. transportationError)
                    const errorEl = document.getElementById (`${name}Error`);
                    if (! selected) {
                        allValid = false;
                        if (errorEl) 
                            errorEl.style.display = 'block';
                        
                    } else {
                        if (errorEl) 
                            errorEl.style.display = 'none';
                        
                    }
                });
                return allValid;
            }
            // ── Collect all form values into a clean JSON object ──
            function collectFormData() {
                const get = (id) => document.getElementById(id) ?. value.trim() ?? '';
                const getRadio = (name) => form.querySelector (`input[name="${name}"]:checked`) ?. value ?? '';
                const getCheckboxes = (name) => [... form.querySelectorAll (`input[name="${name}"]:checked`)].map((el) => el.value);
                return {
                    submittedAt: new Date().toISOString(),
                    // Personal
                    firstName: get('firstName'),
                    lastName: get('lastName'),
                    email: get('email'),
                    phone: get('phone'),
                    city: get('city'),
                    state: get('state'),
                    zipcode: get('zipcode'),
                    // Transportation
                    hasTransportation: getRadio('transportation'),
                    serviceRadius: get('serviceRadius'),
                    // Availability
                    jobsPerWeek: get('jobsPerWeek'),
                    startDate: get('startDate'),
                    // Business & contractor status
                    businessStatus: getRadio('businessStatus'),
                    otherClients: getRadio('otherClients'),
                    hasInsurance: getRadio('insurance'),
                    hasOwnSupplies: getRadio('ownSupplies'),
                    // Experience
                    hasProfessionalExperience: getRadio('experience'),
                    experienceDetails: get('experienceDetails'),
                    comfortableWithPets: getRadio('pets'),
                    serviceTypes: getCheckboxes('serviceTypes'),
                    // Additional
                    whyInterested: get('whyWork'),
                    strengths: get('strengths'),
                    hearAbout: get('hearAbout'),
                    additionalInfo: get('additionalInfo'),
                    // Acknowledgments
                    acknowledgedContractorStatus: document.getElementById('ackContractor') ?. checked ?? false,
                    acknowledgedServiceStandards: document.getElementById('ackStandards') ?. checked ?? false
                };
            }
            // ── Show/hide the loading state on the submit button ──
            function setSubmitting(isSubmitting) {
                const btn = form.querySelector('button[type="submit"]');
                if (isSubmitting) {
                    btn.disabled = true;
                    btn.dataset.originalText = btn.textContent;
                    btn.textContent = 'Submitting…';
                } else {
                    btn.disabled = false;
                    btn.textContent = btn.dataset.originalText ?? 'Submit Application';
                }
            }
            // ── Show a persistent error banner above the submit button ──
            function showSubmitError(message) {
                let banner = document.getElementById('submitErrorBanner');
                if (! banner) {
                    banner = document.createElement('div');
                    banner.id = 'submitErrorBanner';
                    banner.style.cssText = 'background:#fff0f0;border:1px solid #f5c2c7;border-radius:0.6rem;padding:1rem 1.25rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;color:#842029' +
                            ';font-size:0.9rem;';
                    const submitArea = form.querySelector('.text-center.mt-5');
                    form.insertBefore(banner, submitArea);
                }
                banner.textContent = message;
                banner.style.display = 'block';
                banner.scrollIntoView({behavior: 'smooth', block: 'center'});
            }
            function hideSubmitError() {
                const banner = document.getElementById('submitErrorBanner');
                if (banner) 
                    banner.style.display = 'none';
                
            }
            // ── Show the success state ──
            function showSuccess() {
                document
                    .getElementById('form-header')
                    .style
                    .display = 'none';
                form.style.display = 'none';
                document
                    .querySelector('hr')
                    .style
                    .display = 'none';
                document
                    .getElementById('successMessage')
                    .style
                    .display = 'block';
                document.querySelector('.form-container').scrollIntoView({behavior: 'smooth', block: 'start'});
            }
            // ── Main submit handler ──
            form.addEventListener('submit', async function (event) {
                event.preventDefault();
                hideSubmitError();
                // 1. Native browser validation (text, email, select, checkboxes, date fields)
                const nativeValid = form.checkValidity();
                form.classList.add('was-validated');
                // 2. Manual radio group validation
                const radiosValid = validateRadioGroups();
                if (! nativeValid || ! radiosValid) { // Scroll to the first visible invalid field
                    const firstInvalid = form.querySelector('.form-control:invalid, .form-select:invalid, .form-check-input:invalid');
                    if (firstInvalid) {
                        firstInvalid.scrollIntoView({behavior: 'smooth', block: 'center'});
                    }
                    return;
                }
                // 3. Submit to Make.com
                setSubmitting(true);
                try {
                    const payload = collectFormData();
                    const response = await fetch(MAKE_WEBHOOK_URL, {
                        method: 'POST',
                        headers: {
                            'Content-Type': 'application/json'
                        },
                        body: JSON.stringify(payload)
                    });
                    if (! response.ok) {
                        throw new Error (`Server responded with status ${
                            response.status
                        }`);
                    }
                    showSuccess();
                } catch (error) {
                    console.error('Submission error:', error);
                    showSubmitError(
                        'Something went wrong submitting your application. Please try again, or reach out to us directly if the problem continues' +
                        '.'
                    );
                    setSubmitting(false);
                }
            });
            // ── Clear individual radio errors as soon as one is selected ──
            requiredRadioGroups.forEach((name) => {
                form.querySelectorAll (`input[name="${name}"]`).forEach((radio) => {
                    radio.addEventListener('change', () => {
                        const errorEl = document.getElementById (`${name}Error`);
                        if (errorEl) 
                            errorEl.style.display = 'none';
                        
                    });
                });
            });
        </script>
    </main>
{% endblock %}